11/04/2025
Botany project
@Najda Villefranque

===============

gen_REF/ contains the generic drivers (python scripts)
gen_SHORT/ same but just the first day
gen_NONUDGING/ without nudging nor surface parameters
gen_RADFRC/ no radiation => prescribed tendencies (not tested)

REFXXX/   nc forcing files for case XXX using python drivers gen_REF/

input_files/ contains the txt files with the initial profiles and tendencies
  e.g. profiles_member_006.txt = initial profiles for botany member XXX=006

make_cases.sh [configure "sim" parameter inside the script]
  makes ${sim}XXX repos with corresponding inputs and forcings 
  and runs gen_$sim/driver_DEF.py and gen_$sim/driver_SCM.py

To create a new subcase:
- case initialization or forcings: add profiles_member_XXX.txt in input_files/
- model configuration: copy gen_REF/ to new repo and adapt driver_*.py files
